Many foes gather at Amon Fuin in Parth Daenath.\n\nYou should defeat Amon Fuin's forces.
Many foes gather at Amon Fuin in Parth Daenath.\n\nYou should defeat Amon Fuin's forces.

The fortress of Amon Fuin houses the Mordorrim, a cult of evil Men who worship Sauron. Behind the fortress walls wait many who know only loyalty to the Dark Lord and will die for Sauron if necessary. One such powerful foe is the rogmul named Mátrothog. You should defeat this dangerous foe and any others who perform unspeakable rituals at Amon Fuin.
You defeated many foes at the fortress of Amon Fuin, including the vile rogmul Mátrothog, and put an end to some of the unspeakable rituals being performed at that fortress.
